"reborn in the underworld, bound for awakening.’"

msgctxt "mn68:23.5"
msgid "Sā kho panassā bhaginī sāmaṃ diṭṭhā vā hoti anussavassutā vā:"
msgstr ""
"And she’s either seen for herself, or heard from someone else, that that "
"sister"

msgctxt "mn68:23.6"
msgid ""
"‘evaṃsīlā sā bhaginī ahosi itipi, evaṃdhammā sā bhaginī ahosi itipi, "
"evaṃpaññā sā bhaginī ahosi itipi, evaṃvihārinī sā bhaginī ahosi itipi, "
"evaṃvimuttā sā bhaginī ahosi itipī’ti."
msgstr ""
"had such ethics, such qualities, such wisdom, such meditation, or such "
"freedom."

msgctxt "mn68:23.7"
msgid ""
"Sā tassā saddhañca sīlañca sutañca cāgañca paññañca anussarantī tadatthāya "
"cittaṃ upasaṃharati."
msgstr ""
"Recollecting that laywoman’s faith, ethics, learning, generosity, and "
"wisdom, she applies her mind to that end."

msgctxt "mn68:23.8"
msgid "Evampi kho, anuruddhā, upāsikāya phāsuvihāro hoti."
msgstr "That too is how a laywoman lives at ease."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya28"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc28"></a>
msgctxt "mn68:28.1"
msgid ""
"Iti kho, anuruddhā, tathāgato na janakuhanatthaṃ na janalapanatthaṃ na "
"lābhasakkārasilokānisaṃsatthaṃ na ‘iti maṃ jano jānātū’ti sāvake abbhatīte "
"kālaṅkate upapattīsu byākaroti:"
msgstr ""
"So it’s not for the sake of deceiving people or flattering them, nor for the "
"benefit of possessions, honor, or popularity, nor thinking, ‘So let people "
"know about me!’ that the Realized One declares the rebirth of his disciples "
"who have passed away:"

msgctxt "mn68:28.2"
msgid "‘asu amutra upapanno, asu amutra upapanno’ti."
msgstr "‘This one is reborn here, while that one is reborn there.’"

msgctxt "mn68:28.3"
msgid "Santi ca kho, anuruddhā, kulaputtā saddhā uḷāravedā uḷārapāmojjā."
msgstr ""
"Rather, there are respectable persons of faith who are full of joy and "
"gladness."

msgctxt "mn68:28.4"
msgid "Te taṃ sutvā tadatthāya cittaṃ upasaṃharanti."
msgstr "When they hear that, they apply their minds to that end."

msgctxt "mn68:28.5"
msgid "Tesaṃ taṃ, anuruddhā, hoti dīgharattaṃ hitāya sukhāyā”ti."
msgstr "That is for their lasting welfare and happiness.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc29"></a>
msgctxt "mn68:28.6"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "mn68:28.7"
msgid "Attamano āyasmā anuruddho bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandīti."
msgstr ""
"Satisfied, Venerable Anuruddha and friends were happy with what the Buddha "
"said."

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn68:28.8"
msgid "Naḷakapānasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
